org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.zetasql

Class SqlCaseWithValueOperatorRewriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.zetasql.SqlCaseWithValueOperatorRewriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SqlOperatorRewriter

    public class SqlCaseWithValueOperatorRewriter
extends java.lang.Object
implements SqlOperatorRewriter
    Rewrites $case_with_value calls as $case_no_value calls.

    Turns: 

    CASE x
   WHEN w1 THEN t1
   WHEN w2 THEN t2
   ELSE e
   END

    into: 

    CASE
   WHEN x == w1 THEN t1
   WHEN x == w2 THEN t2
   ELSE expr
   END

    Note that the ELSE statement is actually optional, but we don't need to worry about that here because the ZetaSQL analyzer populates the ELSE argument as a NULL literal if it's not specified.
